I"Ì\[E\{\|\hat{\boldsymbol{x}}_{EZF}-\boldsymbol{x}\|^2\}\leq \frac{1}{2}E\{\|\hat{\boldsymbol{x}}_{ZF}-\boldsymbol{x}\|^2\}\]

\[y = \begin{bmatrix}
H_1 &amp; H_2 &amp; \cdots &amp; H_K
\end{bmatrix}
\begin{bmatrix}
	x_1 \\
	x_2 \\
	\vdots \\
	x_K	
\end{bmatrix}+n\]

\[y_i = y-\begin{bmatrix}
H_1 &amp; \cdots &amp; H_{i-1} &amp; H_{i+1} \cdots &amp; H_K
\end{bmatrix}
\begin{bmatrix}
	x_1 \\
	\vdots \\
	x_{i-1} \\
	x_{i+1} \\
	\vdots \\
	x_K	
\end{bmatrix}
=H_ix_i+n\]

